org.tensorics.core.math.operations

Interface CommutativeOperation<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Superinterfaces:
    BinaryFunction<T,T>, BinaryOperation<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CommutativeAssociativeOperation<T>

    public interface CommutativeOperation<T>
extends BinaryOperation<T>
    Represents a binary operation on elements of a set, where the following condition is fullfilled:

    a o b = b o a, with 'a', 'b' being elements of the underlying set, 'o' being the operation.

    See Also:
    http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Commutative_property
